title: DAC7578 Breakout with Included Header Strip
summary: Product photo showing the DAC7578 breakout board and a separate male header strip accessory above it. The board front silkscreen and pin breakout pads are visible.

structured_data.description: A straight male header strip is shown above the board, indicating included solderable pin headers. Board silkscreen again shows DAC7578 labeling and analog output channels 0-7 plus reference and control pins.
